libsai which is build with that image does not implement sai_query_api_version, in this PR i enabled required field for that sai library method saiversion.h header was introduced in in version v1.9.0 in this commit [0b929737](https://github.com/opencomputeproject/SAI/commit/0b929737) which was on Feb 2022, that SAI library used in that build should already implement that API, lets contact marverll to update library with that api, it's 5min change, implementation looks like this: https://github.com/sonic-net/sonic-sairedis/blob/master/vslib/sai_vs_interfacequery.cpp#L208
```c
sai_status_t sai_query_api_version(
        _Out_ sai_api_version_t *version)
{
    *version = SAI_API_VERSION;
    return SAI_STATUS_SUCCESS;
}
```

@lguohan fyi

